mission_data.mission_description: Training Mission for Armada 5. ^^"How to Capture an Enemy Base."

big_message.title: All Your Base
big_message.subtitle1: A mission for Artemis 2.7, by Darrin Bright.
big_message.subtitle2: To reset COMM buttons, set Sensor Power to 0% and Sensor Coolant to 8.

event.name: MenuInit1
event.incoming_comms_text: MISSION OBJECTIVE: Capture all three Torgoth Stations.^^A "Deploy Beacon" button has been added to the COMM station. The COMM OFFICER can use this button to deploy one of your beacons directly behind your ship. This must be done within 1000 km of an enemy base. If the beacon is close enough, then Troop Transports carrying TSN marines will be deployed in your sector, close with the base, and attempt to capture it. ^^If you do not see a "Deploy Beacon" button on the COMM screen, tell ENGINEERING to set Sensors to 0% power and Sensors Coolant to 8. This will reset the COMM buttons.

warning_popup_message.message: COMM: Use 'Deploy Beacon' button within 1000 km of enemy base to capture it.
warning_popup_message.name: Artemis

event.warning_popup_message: MISSION OBJECTIVE: Capture all three Torgoth Stations.^^A "Deploy Beacon" button has been added to the COMM station. The COMM OFFICER can use this button to deploy one of your beacons directly behind your ship. This must be done within 2000 meters of an enemy base. If the beacon is close enough, then Troop Transports carrying TSN marines will be deployed in your sector, close with the base, and attempt to capture it. ^^If you do not see a "Deploy Beacon" button on the COMM screen, tell ENGINEERING to set Sensors to 0% power and Sensors Coolant to 8. This will reset the COMM buttons.
